text: So teachers are supposed to know everything. You're supposed to be equipped and you should know absolutely how to fix everything for your students. But you know what? Sometimes you just don't know everything. And if you find there's been an account created and you're trying to hunt it down and be the detective, it might not just work for you. So we recommend you get in touch with NetSafe or the police. Looking out there, if something were to go wrong on the sea, we'd probably call the lifeguard. Or if you were having a crash on the road you'd call one one one. It's the same if you were online. If you've been digitally harmed, call net safe.
